### ===================================================================
### QALQON AI - ADVOKAT CHAT TO'LIQ TEST (BOSQICH 6)
### ===================================================================
### Oldindan tayyor bo'lishi kerak:
### 1. lawyer.http dagi 1-6 qadamlar bajarilgan (advokat APPROVED holatda)
### 2. Ikkita akkaunt: mijoz (ROLE_USER) va advokat (ROLE_LAWYER)
### ===================================================================

@clientToken = SHU_YERGA_MIJOZ_TOKEN
@lawyerToken = SHU_YERGA_ADVOKAT_TOKEN
@lawyerId = SHU_YERGA_ADVOKAT_PROFILE_ID
@lawyerChatId = SHU_YERGA_CHAT_UUID
@attachId = SHU_YERGA_FAYL_ID

### ===================================================================
### 1-QADAM: MIJOZ LOGIN
### Vazifa: Oddiy foydalanuvchi sifatida token olish
### Eslatma: Javobdan token ni @clientToken ga qo'ying
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: UZ

{
  "username": "MIJOZ_USERNAME",
  "password": "MIJOZ_PAROL"
}

### ===================================================================
### 2-QADAM: MIJOZ - CHAT BOSHLASH + BIRINCHI XABAR
### Vazifa: Tasdiqlangan advokatga birinchi xabar yuborish
### Eslatma: Javobdan chat id ni olish shart emas — keyingi qadamda ro'yxatdan olamiz
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

{
  "lawyerId": {{lawyerId}},
  "message": {
    "content": "Assalomu alaykum, meros masalasida maslahat kerak. Ishni ololasizmi?"
  }
}

### ===================================================================
### 3-QADAM: MIJOZ - QO'SHIMCHA XABAR YUBORISH
### Vazifa: Mavjud chatga ikkinchi xabar yozish
### Eslatma: Avval 7-qadamni bajarib @lawyerChatId ni oling, yoki start javobidan id ni oling
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/{{lawyerChatId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

{
  "content": "Qo'shimcha: otam 2020-yilda vafot etgan, hujjatlar tayyor."
}

### ===================================================================
### 4-QADAM: ADVOKAT LOGIN
### Vazifa: Advokat akkaunti bilan token olish
### Eslatma: Javobdan token ni @lawyerToken ga qo'ying
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: UZ

{
  "username": "ADVOKAT_USERNAME",
  "password": "ADVOKAT_PAROL"
}

### ===================================================================
### 5-QADAM: ADVOKAT - CHATlar RO'YXATI
### Vazifa: Advokat o'z chatlarini ko'radi (ism, rasm, oxirgi xabar bilan)
### Kutilayotgan: clientName, lawyerName, lastMessageContent, lastMessageDate to'ldirilgan
### Eslatma: Ro'yxatdan chat id ni @lawyerChatId ga qo'ying
### ===================================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{lawyerToken}}

### ===================================================================
### 6-QADAM: ADVOKAT - CHAT DETAIL
### Vazifa: Bitta chatning to'liq ma'lumotini ko'rish
### ===================================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/{{lawyerChatId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{lawyerToken}}

### ===================================================================
### 7-QADAM: ADVOKAT - XABARLAR TARIXINI O'QISH
### Vazifa: Chat ichidagi barcha xabarlarni ko'rish
### ===================================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/{{lawyerChatId}}/messages?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{lawyerToken}}

### ===================================================================
### 8-QADAM: ADVOKAT - JAVOB YOZISH
### Vazifa: Mijozga javob berish
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/{{lawyerChatId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{lawyerToken}}

{
  "content": "Assalomu alaykum. Ha, meros bo'yicha yordam bera olaman. Hujjatlarni yuboring."
}

### ===================================================================
### 9-QADAM: MIJOZ - CHAT RO'YXATI (clientName/lawyerName preview)
### Vazifa: Mijoz o'z chatlarini ko'radi
### ===================================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### ===================================================================
### 10-QADAM: MIJOZ - TARIXNI TEKSHIRISH
### Vazifa: Advokat javobi ham tarixda ko'rinishi kerak
### ===================================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/{{lawyerChatId}}/messages?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### ===================================================================
### 11-QADAM: FAYL BILAN XABAR (ixtiyoriy)
### Vazifa: Attach bilan xabar yuborish
### Oldin attach/upload qiling va @attachId ga qo'ying
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/{{lawyerChatId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

{
  "content": "Meros hujjatini ilova qildim.",
  "attachIds": ["{{attachId}}"]
}

### ===================================================================
### 12-QADAM: CHAT YOPISH (MIJOZ yoki ADVOKAT)
### Vazifa: Chat holatini CLOSED qilish
### ===================================================================
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/{{lawyerChatId}}/close
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### ===================================================================
### 13-QADAM: YOPILGAN CHATGA YOZISH — XATO KELISHI KERAK
### Vazifa: CLOSED chatga xabar yuborish bloklanganini tekshirish
### Kutilayotgan: 400 xato — "Lawyer chat yopilgan!"
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/{{lawyerChatId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

{
  "content": "Bu xabar yuborilmasligi kerak — chat yopilgan."
}

### ===================================================================
### 14-QADAM: YOPILGAN CHATNI QAYTA YOPISH — XATO KELISHI KERAK
### Vazifa: Allaqachon CLOSED chatni yopishga urinish
### Kutilayotgan: 400 xato — "Lawyer chat allaqachon yopilgan!"
### ===================================================================
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/{{lawyerChatId}}/close
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### ===================================================================
### 15-QADAM: TASDIQLANMAGAN ADVOKAT BILAN CHAT — XATO KELISHI KERAK
### Vazifa: APPROVED bo'lmagan advokat id si bilan start urinish
### Kutilayotgan: 400 xato — "Advokat hali tasdiqlanmagan!"
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

{
  "lawyerId": 99999,
  "message": {
    "content": "Bu chat boshlanmasligi kerak."
  }
}
